<\\/h3><p style=\\\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; white-space: normal;\\\">At 1mg, our goal is to make healthcare understandable, accessible and affordable in India. We set out on our journey in 2015, and have come a long way&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; white-space: normal;\\\">since then. Along the way, we have been conferred with prestigious titles like&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-weight: 700;\\\">BML Munjal Award for \'Business Excellence through Learning and&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; white-space: normal;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 700;\\\">Development\', Best Online Pharmacy in India Award<\\/span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-weight: 700;\\\">Top 50 venture in The Smart CEO-Startup50 India.<\\/span>&nbsp;We have been selected as the only&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; white-space: normal;\\\">company from across the globe for<span style=\\\"font-weight: 700;\\\">&nbsp;SD#3 \\\"Health &amp; Well Being for all\\\" by Unreasonable group, US State Department.<\\/span>&nbsp;In 2019 alone we received three&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Clear Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; white-space: normal;\\\">awards including the<span style=\\\"font-weight: 700;\\\">&nbsp;BMW Simply Unstoppable Award.<\\/span><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":